title: Dementia looks different in brains of Hispanics

title_detail.value: Dementia looks different in brains of Hispanics

summary: A major new study has uncovered dramatic differences in the brains of Hispanics with a dementia diagnosis compared with those of non-Hispanic whites and of African Americans.
